                  </persName>
             depos'd, That she lay in the same Room, in the Bed with her Mother, and spoke to him at one o' Clock, and that he was not out all Night, other Witnesses deposing to the like Effect, and he having a good Character, the Jury <rs id="t17281016-42-verdict207" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17281016-42-verdict207" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
